introduction 1 in this proceeding, on 8 august 2005 colin nicol was appointed receiver and manager of all the property of guiseppe antonio mercorella (with one exception), and the property of the unregistered managed investment scheme operated by mr mercorella (the scheme) as well as liquidator of the scheme.
on 3 august 2006 samuel davies was appointed jointly with mr nicol as receiver and manager of the property of mr mercorella and the property of the scheme, and as liquidator of the scheme and as liquidator of the scheme companies.